# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/

# --- Build outputs ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/

# --- Env files (never commit secrets) ---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.production
**/.env.development
!**/.env.example
!**/docker-compose.*.example.yml

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# --- OS files ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- IDEs / editors ---
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Vite / tooling caches ---
**/.vite/
**/.cache/
**/.turbo/

# --- Coverage ---
**/coverage/

# --- Local database and volumes ---
**/data/
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/postgres_data/

# --- Docker ---
.docker/
docker-compose.override.yml

# --- Misc ---
*.bak
*.tmp
*.old
